name: Insutech Corporation
overview:
Established in the year 1981, we, Insutech Corporation have An ISO 9001:2008 Certified Company carved a niche for ourselves in the sphere of manufacturing and supplying a comprehensive range of DSL, Spring Buffers, Cable Trolleys, Rail Clamps, Rail Pads and Drag Chains. In our broad range, we offer products such as Light Duty Stretched Wire, Closed C Track, I- Beam System, Angle DSL System and Shrouded Bar System.

Our Team: The success and growth of our organization is propelled by the relentless efforts of our talented and experienced professionals, which are selected through rigorous recruitment processes. Having a thorough knowledge of the concerned discipline, these professionals work in perfect harmony to achieve the set objective of the organization. Moreover, the proficiency of our professionals not only aids in offering innovative solution but also in maintaining timeliness in deliveries.

Our Infrastructure: In order to constantly nurture our innovative capabilities and offer best in industry products, we have established a modern infrastructure facility for ourselves. Fully equipped with advanced machines and technologies, the unit is evenly segregated into various divisions such as manufacturing, quality testing, research and development and allied.

Our Products: DSL System Rail Clamp & Pad Drag Chain Spring Buffer
